@InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5073
@token = 

### 🔐 Login (obtener JWT)
POST {{InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 👆 Guarda automáticamente el token en la variable {{token}}

###

# 🧾 GET - Todos los productos (requiere autenticación)
GET {{InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress}}/api/Inventory/products
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# 🧪 GET - Un producto por ID
GET {{InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress}}/api/Inventory/products/P001
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ➕ POST - Agregar un nuevo producto
POST {{InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress}}/api/Inventory/products/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "code": "P003",
  "name": "USB-C Hub",
  "category": "Peripherals",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 45.50
}

###

# 🗑️ DELETE - Eliminar un producto
DELETE {{InventorySystem_webapi_HostAddress}}/api/Inventory/products/P003
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
